This is how to correct_bracketing of brackets:
  Remember that balance is 0
  Remember that ok is yes
  Do this brackets's length times:
    When balance is less than 0, then:
      Remember that ok is no
      Leave the loop
    End when
    When item i in brackets is "<", then:
      Increase balance
    But, if not:
      Decrease balance
    End when
    Increase i
  End do
  When ok is no, then:
    The answer is 0
  End when
  When balance is 0, then:
    The answer is 1
  But, if not:
    The answer is 0
  End when
